#: ../../source/language/php/disablefunc.rst:2
msgid "Disable Functions"
msgstr "Disable Functions"

#: ../../source/language/php/disablefunc.rst:5
msgid "机制实现"
msgstr "Implementation Mechanism"

#: ../../source/language/php/disablefunc.rst:6
msgid ""
"PHP中Disable Function的实现是在php-src/Zend/Zend-"
"API.c中。PHP在启动时，读取配置文件中禁止的函数，逐一根据禁止的函数名调用 ``zend_disable_function`` "
"来实现禁止的效果。"
msgstr ""
"PHP implements Disable Function in php-src/Zend/Zend-API.c. During startup, "
"PHP reads the disabled functions from the configuration file and calls "
"``zend_disable_function`` for each disabled function name to enforce the "
"restriction."

#: ../../source/language/php/disablefunc.rst:8
msgid "这个函数根据函数名在内置函数列表中找到对应的位置并修改掉，当前版本的代码如下："
msgstr "This function finds the corresponding entry in the built-in function list by function name and modifies it. The current version of the code is shown below:"

#: ../../source/language/php/disablefunc.rst:26
msgid "和函数的实现方式类似，disable classes也是这样实现的"
msgstr "Similar to the function implementation, disable classes is implemented in the same way."

#: ../../source/language/php/disablefunc.rst:48
msgid ""
"因为这个实现机制的原因，在PHP启动后通过 ``ini_set`` 来修改 ``disable_functions`` 或 "
"``disable_classes`` 是无效的。"
msgstr ""
"Because of this implementation mechanism, changing ``disable_functions`` or "
"``disable_classes`` with ``ini_set`` after PHP has started is ineffective."

